description: Larat orchid is one of the flowers of Indonesian identity, especially in Maluku.This plant has the scientific name Dendrobium phalaenopsis. Larat orchids have two similar names, namely Vappodes phalaenopsis and Dendrobium bigibbum. This beautiful flowering plant belongs to the Orchidaceae family. Larat orchids are rare and protected plants. The name Larat Orchid is taken from the name Larat Island in the Maluku Islands
